OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772881499
OL,3,CIndonesia moves to ban social media
OL,4,Cfor under-16s
OL,6,FIndonesia is to become the latest
OL,7,Fcountry to ban children under the age
OL,8,Fof 16 from using social media.
OL,10,FA new government regulation will
OL,11,Fprohibit children from making accounts
OL,12,Fon digital platforms, such as YouTube,
OL,13,FTikTok, Facebook, Instagram, Threads,
OL,14,FX, Bigo Live and Roblox.
OL,16,FThe law will be implemented gradually,
OL,17,Fstarting from March 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
