OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772881499
OL,3,CIndonesia moves to ban social media
OL,4,Cfor under-16s
OL,6,F"The basis is clear. Our children face
OL,7,Fincreasingly real threats, from
OL,8,Fexposure to pornography,
OL,9,Fcyberbullying, online fraud, and most
OL,10,Fimportantly addiction," communication
OL,11,Fand digital affairs minister Meutya
OL,12,FHafid said.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,F"The government is here so that
OL,20,Fparents no longer have to fight alone
OL,21,Fagainst the giant of algorithms."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
