OL,3,CIndonesia moves to ban social media
OL,4,Cfor under-16s
OL,6,FSeveral governments have imposed
OL,7,Frestrictions on children using social
OL,8,Fmedia in recent months as welfare and
OL,9,Fsafety concerns mount around the world.
OL,11,FAustralia became the first country to
OL,12,Fimplement a ban on under-16s in
OL,13,FDecember, followed by Malaysia, whose
OL,14,Fban came into force this year. Similar
OL,15,Flaws are also in the works in France,
OL,16,FSpain and Portugal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
