OL,3,CIndonesia moves to ban social media
OL,4,Cfor under-16s
OL,6,FCompanies like Snapchat, Instagram,
OL,7,FFacebook, and TikTok say they have
OL,8,Fmeasures in place to verify the age of
OL,9,Fchildren, as well as ways to restrict
OL,10,Ftheir access to harmful content.
OL,12,FA proposed amendment to the Children's
OL,13,FWellbeing and Schools Bill that would
OL,14,Fhave issued such a ban was defeated in
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
