OL,3,CIndonesia moves to ban social media
OL,4,Cfor under-16s
OL,6,FOn Monday, a government consultation
OL,7,Fon a ban was opened for the general
OL,8,Fpublic to share their view. It calls
OL,9,Ffor parents and people under the age
OL,10,Fof 21 in particular to respond, and
OL,11,Fwill close on May 26.
